</P>
<P>
   &UR; DAVID-LETTERMAN LATE SHOW TOP TEN &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; ``Words That Kind of Rhyme with Elway'' &LR;
</P>
<P>
   10. Elyaw
</P>
<P>
   9. Ebay
</P>
<P>
