(For use by NYTimes News Service clients)  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following stories
today for use by NYTimes News Service clients. They will move in
the ``e'' entertainment news file. For questions, contact Bob
McCarthy at the Daily News, (818) 713-3665. 
. 
ELFMAN-PLAY (Los Angeles) _ Jenna Elfman has a hit TV show and two
highly anticipated movies coming out. She's just won a Golden Globe
and a TV Guide award. So what's she doing working and rehearsing in
``Visions and Lovers: Variations on a Theme,'' a one-act play at a
99-seat equity-waiver theater? ``I want to surprise people. I want
to surprise myself,'' says the ``Dharma and Greg'' star. By Rob
Lowman. 
 
 
