<HEADLINE>
BOSTON POPS CROSSES OVER WITH GRAMMY-NOMINATED `THE CELTIC ALBUM`
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By FRED SHUSTER 
c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News 
  
