<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-02 19:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9104 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOLBROOKE-ETHICS-NYT &LR;      02-02 0757
