Post-Intelligencer in the morning field. The amended agreement also
includes a 50-year extension of the joint operating agreement to
Dec. 31, 2083, and provides an increase in the Post-Intelligencer's
economic participation from the current 32 percent to 40 percent.
By The Hearst Newspapers. (Already filed.)
